MBALI KHANYILE OWESIFAZANE ufile ngemva kokudubuleka esifubeni ngesikhathi amadoda amabili abehlome ethe shi ebamba inkunzi esitolo sezimpahla zokugqoka esisemgwaqweni uGopalall Hurbans, oThongathi, ngoLwesihlanu ntambama. Kuthiwa owesifazane ushonele khona lapho esitolo okuthiwa umnikazi waso ngowase-Ethiopia. Kuthiwa womabili amadoda athathe ngesivu ngemva kokudubula umufi. Okhulumela iReaction Unit, uMnuz Prem  Balram, uthe baphuthume endaweni yobugebengu kulandela ukuthola umbiko ngabo-5 ntambama. “Sifike eseshonile obedubuleke esifubeni. Amadoda amabili abephanga kuthiwa abalekile ngemva kokudubula. Imbangela yokubulawa kukamufi ayikaziwa. Kuvulwe icala lokubulala,” kusho uBalram. Okhulumela amphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uColonel Thembeka Mbele, ukuqinisekisile ukudutshulwa kowesifazane (42)  esitolo sezimpahla zokugqoka. “Abasebenzi ababili besifazane abaphonswe imibuzo mayelana nokwenzekile bathe bebematasa nomsebenzi ngesikhathi bezwa kuqhuma kabili isibhamu kwabaleka wonke umuntu obesesitolo. Yonke into ibibukeka iphelele esitolo. Imali, amaselula nezikhwama zabasebenzi kakuthathwanga,” kusho uColonel Mbele.